oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Couples on bridge near springs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three couples walking along a scenic trail by a spring near Monterey, Tennessee. The men wear hats and the women are in dresses. They appear to be crossing a wood bridge, above edge of spring, and several have their hands resting on a bridge rail.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
